data.description: This home is eligible for our down payment grant of up to $7,000. This is free money, you only need 1% of the purchase price or $2,970 to own this home! Meticulously maintained home in a tranquil neighborhood.  Home Boasts a new metal roof, new AC, water heater 2018, and new waterproof luxury vinyl plank flooring. The many large windows allow tons of natural light fill the home, and the accordion style hurricane shutters provide maximum protection and peace of mind.     Large eat-in kitchen with numerous cabinets providing ample storage for all your culinary needs.. Updates to kitchen include custom maple wood cabinets, granite counter tops, and energy efficient stainless steel appliances. Thoughtfully appointed  master bedroom with walk-in closet located opposite  other bedr tiled shower.  Two additional bedrooms that are perfectly sized for your families growing needs. Hall bath has granite countertop, maple wood cabinets, and has tube/shower with wall to ceiling tile. Enjoy the Florida weather relaxing in your large 375sq ft screened in porch overlooking the lush landscaping on your oversized fenced corner lot. Don't miss out and schedule your showing today!
